    T.61  X11 Keysym  ISO8859/1 ASCII
    ---------------------------------
    \f1   ae          0xE6      {
    \e1   AE          0xC6      [ 
    \f9   oslash      0xF8      |
    \e9   Ooblique    0xD8      \
    \caa  aring       0xE5      }
    \caA  Aring       0xC5      ]

